Some [[image:image.png||alt="alternative text" width="250" data-xwiki-image-style-alignment="center" data-xwiki-image-label="This is the caption"]]

[[Caption for my logo>>image:logo.png||alt="my logo" width="100" data-xwiki-image-style-alignment="end"]]